Task 4: Predicting Insurance Claim Amounts

Estimating medical insurance claim amounts using Machine Learning.

Objective:
● Train a Linear Regression model to predict charges.
● Visualize how BMI, age, and smoking status impact insurance charges.
● Evaluate model performance using MAE and RMSE.

Skills:
● Regression modeling
● Feature correlation and visualization
● Error evaluation using MAE and RMSE

Results:
● Accuracy: 78% (R² Score)
● Error Metrics: MAE ($4,181) and RMSE ($5,796)
● Top Influencers: Smoking Status, Age, and BMI.
